quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  91,1,"Mi wooɗndarii na'ange e mbeeta mum."
  91,2,"Mi wooɗndirii lewru sundu rewii e henge."
  91,3,"Mi wooɗndirii ñalawma sombo huñciima."
  91,4,"Mi wooɗndarii jehma si mbo arii e niɓɓidde."
  91,5,"Mi wooɗndirii kammu e mahdi mammba."
  91,6,"Mi wooɗndirii leydi no ndi wertarii."
  91,7,"Mi wooɗndirii fittaandu e ko foocci ndu."
  91,8,"O ɓannginani ndu faajiraagal e kulol alla."
  91,9,"Malaama noon oon laaɓɓinɗo ndu."
  91,10,"Ko goongo perti oon mutnuɗo fittaandu mum e goopi."
  91,11,"Samuudinkooɓe ɓeen njeddiino nulaaɓe ɓeen."
  91,12,"Tuma nde nelaa ɓurɗo hiiteede e mu' en."
  91,13,"Nelaaɗo Alla wi ɗum ko ngeloobo njarla ɗaleeba e njaram mabba."
  91,14,"Ɓe njeddi ɗum ɓe mborii ba, joomiraawo ommbi e dow mu'en lepte sabu bakkatuuji mum en o huɓtadi ɓe lepte."
  91,15,"Te o hulaani battane mum."
  92,1,"Mi wooɗndarii jemma si mbo arii e niɓɓidde."
  92,2,"Mi wooɗndirii ñalawma sombo huñciima."
  92,3,"Mi wooɗndirii ko o tagi ko gorel e deyel."
  92,4,"Pellet golle mon heɗe ceerti."
  92,5,"Si tawi ko oon tottirɗo o reenti."
  92,6,"O gooŋɗini baraaji golle mum."
  92,7,"Ma min newnan mo kala jam e newaare."
  92,8,"Si tawi ko oon ngammbuɗo o yondinii."
  92,9,"O yeddi njoɓdi.(aljanna)."
  92,10,"Ma min newnan ɗum saɗteende."
  92,11,"Nafataa ɗum jawdi makko si o saami e yiite."
  92,12,"Ko e amen peewal woni."
  92,13,"Ko minen woodani nguurndam La'akara yo aduna."
  92,14,"Njeertin mi on jayngol huɓɓoowol."